Package: noodles
Title: R Utiliies for Gartner
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: 
    person("J.J.", "Moncus", , "jj.moncus@gartner.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A grabbag of useful functions and data structures useful for 
  analyses of Gartner data assets The package is designed specifically for the 
  Customer Service and Support PPR team but is broadly useful for anyone
  at Gartner hoping to do routine data analysis in R.
